          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Entity uses this option as a reference coordinate space during transform conversion.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Depending on the coordinate space that a caller entity is parented under, and whether there is an immersive space open, some transform conversion case can be inapplicable. Check out each case for more information.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
